title: Ceiling Paper, 1905–15
medium: Machine-printed on paper, textured ground, mica, liquid
inscribed: Printed in selvedge: "Wm. H. Mairs & Co. 2635"
description:
Overall waving scrolls pattern with individual pink roses with foliage. Ground is cream and embossed with a treillage and flower design. Printed in gold mica, green, pinks, white, and grey. 
Printed in selvedge: "Wm. H. Mairs & Co. 2635"
